for streams where timestamps are monotonously ascending\\n\\n2. TextInputFormat (I/O Format Class)\\n   - Location: flink-streaming-java/src/main/java/org/apache/flink/streaming/api/legacy/io/TextInputFormat.java\\n   - Type: Extends DelimitedInputFormat<String>\\n   - Deprecation: @Deprecated with javadoc message\\n   - Recommended Replacement: \\\"FLIP-27 FileSource and Sink-V2 FlinkSink\\\"\\n   - Deprecation Note: \\\"This class should be removed if we drop the supports for read/write via input/output format in DataStream api.\\\"\\n\\n3. TextOutputFormat (I/O Format Class)\\n   - Location: flink-streaming-java/src/main/java/org/apache/flink/streaming/api/legacy/io/TextOutputFormat.java\\n   - Type: Generic class extends FileOutputFormat<T>\\n   - Deprecation: @Deprecated with javadoc message\\n   - Recommended Replacement: \\\"FLIP-27 FileSource and Sink-V2 FlinkSink\\\"\\n   - Deprecation Note: \\\"This class should be removed if we drop all supports for InputFormat and OutputFormat\\\"\\n\\nDEPRECATED TEST UTILITIES (3 test harness classes):\\n\\n4. OneInputStreamTaskTestHarness\\n   - Location: flink-streaming-java/src/test/java/org/apache/flink/streaming/runtime/tasks/OneInputStreamTaskTestHarness.java\\n   - Deprecation: @Deprecated\\n   - Recommended Replacement: \\\"StreamTaskMailboxTestHarness and StreamTaskMailboxTestHarnessBuilder\\\"\\n   - Note: \\\"Do not add new code using this test harness\\\"\\n\\n5. StreamTaskTestHarness\\n   - Location: flink-streaming-java/src/test/java/org/apache/flink/streaming/runtime/tasks/StreamTaskTestHarness.java\\n   - Deprecation: @Deprecated\\n   - Recommended Replacement: \\\"StreamTaskMailboxTestHarness and StreamTaskMailboxTestHarnessBuilder\\\"\\n   - Note: \\\"Do not add new code using this test harness\\\"\\n\\n6. TwoInputStreamTaskTestHarness\\n   - Location: flink-streaming-java/src/test/java/org/apache/flink/streaming/runtime/tasks/TwoInputStreamTaskTestHarness.java\\n   - Deprecation: @Deprecated\\n   - Recommended Replacement: \\\"StreamTaskMailboxTestHarness and StreamTaskMailboxTestHarnessBuilder\\\"\\n   - Note: \\\"Do not add new code using this test harness\\\"\\n\\nSUMMARY:\\nThe search identified 3 main deprecated DataStream API classes in flink-streaming-java/src/main/ that match the focus criteria (timestamp extractors and I/O format classes), plus 3 deprecated test utility classes in flink-streaming-java/src/test/. The I/O format classes (TextInputFormat and TextOutputFormat) recommend migrating to FLIP-27 FileSource and Sink-V2 APIs. The AscendingTimestampExtractor has no specific replacement mentioned in its deprecation javadoc.\"\n}\n",
